Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.76,0:21:40.57,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(280,280)\blur3}便迎来大家沐浴阳光的笑脸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.77,0:21:45.70,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(280,280)\blur3}亲如一家
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.32,0:21:48.66,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\an3\fad(280,280)\blur3}自然而然
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.90,0:21:50.87,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(280,280)\blur3}永不分离
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.49,0:21:53.16,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\an3\fad(280,280)\blur3}相守相望
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.08,0:21:58.67,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\an1\fad(280,280)\blur3}采撷点滴温馨 探索奇妙世界
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.75,0:22:01.63,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(280,280)\blur3}天空近在咫尺
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.71,0:22:06.55,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(280,280)\blur3}花儿悄然绽放
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.55,0:22:11.89,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(280,280)\blur3}静静流淌的日子竟也如此芬芳可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.01,0:22:21.90,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(280,280)\blur3}期待丰收结果时 用心栽培每一日
